QuestData.Title: Heroic: All Is Well That Ends Well
QuestData.Description: We'd best hurry now, $n. We're going to have to transmit the reply-code from Dalaran.$B$BTake it to Rhonin, I will meet you there.
QuestData.LogDescription: Take the Reply-Code Alpha to Rhonin in Dalaran.
QuestData.RewardText: You're here. Let us hope this works. For all our sakes.
